
 .jsp ->  .java
 .java ->.class
 .class  -> load the class
 create the object of the class
 init
 service
 destroy

Lifecycle of servlet
1. instantiation
2. init
3. service
4. destroy

 LifCycle of JSP:
 1. translation
 2. compilation
 3. loading
 4. instantiation
 5. jspInit
 6. jspService
 7. jspDestroy


tag in jsp
--------------------------
<%  %> scriptlet
<%! %> declaration
<%= %> expression
<%@ %> directive
    1. page <%@ page %>
      attribute_name
        import
        isErrorPage="true"  default false
        errorPage="page_to be display during exception"

    2. include  <%@ include %>
    3. taglib   <%@ taglib %>
<%--   %>  jsp comment
<!--   -->  html comment
jspAction tag
  <jsp:useBean>
  <jsp:setProperty>
  <jsp:getProperty>
  <jsp:forward>
implicit object
-----------------
request         HttpServletRequest
response        HttpServletResponse
session         HttpSession
application     ServletContext
config          ServletConfig
exception       Throwable
out             JspWriter
pageContext     pageContext
page            Object


scope in jsp
--------------
page
request
session
  application


el implicit object
------------------
requestScope
pageScope
sessionScope
applicationScope
header
headerValues
param
paramValues


${requestScope.a}  => request.getAttribute("a")





